]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he heated"},{"kind":"text","text":"an iron nail, (ISk, K,) and a piece of iron, (ISk, S,) &c., in the fire: (ISk:) one should not say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaY","text_ar":"حَمَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this sense; (ISk, S, Msb, TA;) app., in chaste speech; for otherwise one does say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaY Al$~aYo'a fiY Aln~aAri","text_ar":"حَمَى الشَّىْءَ فِى النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put the thing into the thing into the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and so heated it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmY Almiysama","text_ar":"احمى المِيسَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmY Ealayohi","text_ar":"احمى عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He kindled fire upon the branding-iron"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and so heated it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmAhu EalaY AlqitaAli","text_ar":"احماهُ عَلَى القِتَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He excited him to ardour for fight"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HrD","text_ar":"حرض"},{"kind":"text","text":"; &c.)"}],"source_refs":["Lh","K","Msb","ISk","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}